title: Rocksmith 2014 Custom DLC folder with over 500 CDLC
description:
Title doesn't begin to describe this collection. I have personally downloaded each of the custom songs in this package from http://forums.smithyanvil.com/index.php . I found this site a year ago for the first Rocksmith and they are still at it for this one. I love this place and recommend it to everyone. Anyway on to the package. 

THIS IS FOR ROCKSMITH 2014 PLAYERS WHO HAVE A SKIDROW CRACKED VERSION OF THE GAME ONLY!!!

Now that that's out the way here is what follows. This is a collection of over 500 CDLC from smithyanvil members who contribute their time to making these available for free. Smithyanvil does not support the cracked version of the game so no asking for help in that matter. This also contains the original rocksmith 2012 Official DLC and the songs that were originally included in Rocksmith 2012. This also contains All of the current up to the MUSE pack and Golden Bomber pack just a few weeks ago. Unfortunately there was no Christmas pack this year.... 

Install Instructions

Copy Contents of Rocksmith 2014 Custom DLC folder into your Root Rocksmith 2014 folder Overwriting any files that need to be overwritten. 

This pack contains such artists as 

Linkin Park
Limp Bizkit
Coheed and Cambria
Nirvana
Metallica

and many many more... Way to many to list here. 

This SKIDROW.ini file is updated to include all of the official songs that have been released up until 12/26/2013
